dct_title_s: [Maps from Lynch's Narrative of the United States' expedition to the River Jordan and the Dead Sea]
dct_description_sm: under the command of W. F. Lynch ; P.S. Duval's steam lith. press.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Bar scale on map given in "Miles".
Shows topography, drainage, vegetation, places of historical interest.
Appears in Lynch's Narrative of the United States' expedition to the river Jordan and the Dead Sea, new and corr. ed. Philadelphia : Lea and Blanchard, 1849.
